          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-Pop-GearPAirExternal.ipp" align="left" scale="100.00%" padding="0 2 0 0" figurelistinclude="0"><title>External Gear Mesh</title><caption><![CDATA[External Mesh]]></caption></image><image src="MD-Pop-GearPairInternall.ipp" align="left" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Internal Mesh]]></caption></image></para>
