      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Element">Gear-Pair</text> is two gear-wheels in mesh.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">External Mesh</text> : two gear-wheels have gear-teeth that point outwards from the center-of-rotation.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Internal Mesh</text> : one gear-wheels has gear-teeth that point inwards towards the center-of-rotation.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear-Train</text>: The <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Driven-Gear</text> of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear-Pair-A</text> is the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Driving-Gear</text> of <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear-Pair-B</text>. and the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Driven-Gear</text> of <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear-Pair-B</text> drives/is the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Driving-Gear</text> of <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Gear-Pair-C</text>, and the ...</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddGearPair">Add Gear-Pair</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-GearPair">Gear-Pair dialog</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Gear-Module">Gear Module</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Gear-Module-Standard">Industry Standard Gear Modules</link></para>
        </td>
